import React from 'react';
import { Header, Icon, Segment, Grid, Modal, Button, Embed } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import Vikings from '../Video/Vikings.mp4';
import Got from '../Video/got.mp4';
import ReactPlayer from 'react-player'


const HeaderPart = () => {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Grid columns="equal" inverted>
                <Grid.Row textAlign='right'>
                    <Grid.Column>
                        11
                    </Grid.Column>
                    <Grid.Column>
                        <Segment color='red' inverted>
                            <Modal trigger={<Button>Basic Modal</Button>} basic size='large'>
                                {/* <Modal.Content>
                                </Modal.Content> */}
                                <Segment color='red' inverted>
                                    <ReactPlayer url={Vikings}
                                        autoPlay
                                        playing
                                        loop
                                        width='100%'
                                        controls
                                        left="50%"
                                    />
                                </Segment>
                                <Modal.Actions>
                                    <Button basic color='red' inverted>
                                        <Icon name='remove' /> No
                                </Button>
                                    <Button color='green' inverted>
                                        <Icon name='checkmark' /> Yes
                                </Button>
                                </Modal.Actions>
                            </Modal>
                        </Segment>
                    </Grid.Column>
                </Grid.Row>
            </Grid>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default HeaderPart;
